\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 Cultural Legacy\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Logan Roy became a cultural shorthand for a certain kind of patriarch -- brilliant, brutal, self-made, and ultimately tragic. Brian Cox's performance is almost entirely internal, communicating enormous things through stillness and restraint. The character sparked widespread discussion about power, inheritance, masculinity, and whether someone shaped by trauma can ever truly love without destroying what they love.\
